thread.section_title: Optimalprint Reviews | Customer Service Reviews of Optimalprint | optimalprint.ca
thread.title: Britt N

author: Britt N
title: Britt N
text:
This was by far the least expensive site to create cards in Canadian funds. The website was easy to navigate and create the product you wish. The quality was tremendous with thick card stock and beautiful photo quality. We placed our order on a Saturday evening and it was on our doorstep on Tuesday. We live in a remote community and often we have issues with mail but not with Optimal Print. I recommended Optimal Print to some friends in the community and three others ordered that week :)
Great experience overall.
